{"tid":1025083,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今日同女神跑渣馬10K, 跑唔夠10分鐘就要入救護站","createTime":"2019-02-17T05:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T15:47:34.000Z","uid":35361,"like":42,"dislike":325,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"8fcfe5454fffd18d607d0d559a94deae326c070c","tid":1025083,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T05:39:23.000Z","msg":"今日同女神一齊跑渣馬10K, 同行仲有佢個女仔fd, 同3個MK仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開始跑之前, 大家就一齊搵左個位熱身,<br />\n咁果幾個MK仔裝備又多又緊身衫又緊身褲, 但又瘦猛猛咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地一邊熱身一邊係咁講咩尋晚睇雙曼睇通頂, 又話咩好攰 一陣又話唔知跑唔跑得完<br />\n咁我聽到心入面暗笑, 我尋晚20:00就訓 休息充足, 又一早已經開始操緊 keep住每次都跑1個鐘左右, 心諗今次仲唔係女神面前威返次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開跑果時MK, 女神, 女神朋友一邊跑一邊有傾有講, 我開頭都追到佢地, 但係就唔夠氣傾計, 跑跑下 連追都追唔到, 10分鐘之後 狂扯氣 頂唔順去救護站........... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後女神whatsapp send左句: 冇事嗎? 我們走先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我再whatsapp佢 佢冇應機了.... 我仲係ig見到佢地跑完食茶記........hashtag #5人輕鬆跑10K<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我明明3個月前開始操, 每星期跑2次 1個鐘.. 每次跑10個運動場圈<br />\n我計佢1圈1K到, 10個圈都10K啦, 平時跑都掂, 今日唔知做咩...<br />\n可能學新聞話齋, 天氣太濕, 影響發揮"},{"pid":"e26af68b9196cec1f4a8132bef3a2851e4a83ee3","tid":1025083,"uid":120101,"like":252,"dislike":8,"score":244,"quote":{"pid":"8fcfe5454fffd18d607d0d559a94deae326c070c","tid":1025083,"uid":35361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T05:39:23.000Z","msg":"今日同女神一齊跑渣馬10K, 同行仲有佢個女仔fd, 同3個MK仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開始跑之前, 大家就一齊搵左個位熱身,<br />\n咁果幾個MK仔裝備又多又緊身衫又緊身褲, 但又瘦猛猛咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地一邊熱身一邊係咁講咩尋晚睇雙曼睇通頂, 又話咩好攰 一陣又話唔知跑唔跑得完<br />\n咁我聽到心入面暗笑, 我尋晚20:00就訓 休息充足, 又一早已經開始操緊 keep住每次都跑1個鐘左右, 心諗今次仲唔係女神面前威返次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開跑果時MK, 女神, 女神朋友一邊跑一邊有傾有講, 我開頭都追到佢地, 但係就唔夠氣傾計, 跑跑下 連追都追唔到, 10分鐘之後 狂扯氣 頂唔順去救護站........... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後女神whatsapp send左句: 冇事嗎? 我們走先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我再whatsapp佢 佢冇應機了.... 我仲係ig見到佢地跑完食茶記........hashtag #5人輕鬆跑10K<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces